title: "Wheeler: Reliable, trustworthy, trackable AI workflows for science"
abstract: >-
  A Claude Code-native research assistant with a provenance-tracked
  knowledge graph that makes every AI-produced result traceable back to
  the exact script, data, and parameters that produced it.
